data.description: Welcome to West Lancaster adjacent to Antelope Valley College Excellent location to live. This Beautiful Pool/Spa Home features SunRun Solar Panels (PAID OFF AT CLOSE OF ESCROW). High vaulted ceiling, Gorgeous wood floors, Custom paint throughout the home, Special made granite counter tops, Bright white kitchen cabinets, Window views outdoor area. Gas burning fireplace in the family room. 4 clean bedrooms with ceiling fans up stairs and 1bonus room that can be the 5th downstairs with a full bath. Backyard boasts a beautiful landscape with pool/spa area with artificial grass and large covered patio for Summer shades. Includes storage sheds and a gated dog run plus more to see.Property is located at the end of the Cul-De-Sac Street with a Huge Drive for Multiple Car Parking. CALL NOW FOR MORE DETAILS....
